Transferring a Call Using the KX-TDE or KX-NCP

00:00:12.530 --> 00:00:17.090
While on conversation, you can transfer a
call to another person using the Transfer

00:00:17.090 --> 00:00:23.810
feature button on your telephone. To transfer
a call, press the 'Transfer' button.

00:00:23.810 --> 00:00:26.570
The caller is automatically placed on hold.

00:00:26.570 --> 00:00:33.570
Dial the extension number where you want the
call to be transferred.

00:00:35.489 --> 00:00:39.750
You can wait for an answer and announce the
call or simply hang up by pressing the 'Speaker

00:00:39.750 --> 00:00:42.760
phone' button.

00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:48.870
The call gets transferred to the given extension
number.

